## 6. Key Hyperparameters to Sweep

| Hyperparameter | Stage | Values to Try | What It Controls |
|---|---|---|---|
| lag time τ | TAE (Stage 2) | 1, 5, 10, 20, 50 ns | Slow vs fast dynamical modes |
| latent_dim | TAE, GNN | 2, 4, 8 | Dimensionality of conformational space |
| edge cutoff | GNN | 6Å, 8Å, 10Å | Graph connectivity |
| T (diffusion steps) | DDPM | 500, 1000 | Forward process length |
| guidance_scale | CFG | 1.0, 3.0, 5.0, 7.0 | State specificity vs ensemble diversity |
| k (clusters) | k-means | 3, 5, 7 | Number of conformational states |

